description:
Well I havn't make A new Mindick video in A while so here you go. Have you ever wondered what happened when Manic meet Mindy's dad for the first time? Yah me to. (Well... I already knew since I partly own sonic underground but whatever :P) I hope you all enjoy. 

Bardonic video will come next. I can't stray to far from the good yknow?
